    "The paper is structured as follows.",
    "In Section 2, we present a literature review on the state of the art of education to AI.",
    "In Section 3, we analyze the body of literature in the field of philosophy to identify key epistemological issues related to AI and, in particular, ML and deep learning.",
    "Then, in Section 4, we present the design principles that guided the design of the module on AI, focusing in particular on the epistemic insights that we want to foster.",
    "Section 5 is devoted to illustrating the articulation of the module in preparation for the work we do in Section 6: here, we present the epistemic insights raised by the imperative procedural, declarative logic, and deep learning paradigms when confronting the same operational task, i.e., how to make a computer play tic-tac-toe."
